OL,5, Wasted wind power will add #40 to the  
OL,6, average UK household's electricity bill
OL,7, in 2023, according to a think tank.    
OL,9,FThat figure could increase to #150 in  
OL,10,F2026, Carbon Tracker has estimated.    
OL,12,FWhen it is very windy, the grid cannot 
OL,13,Fhandle the extra power generated. Wind 
OL,14,Ffarms are paid to switch off and       
OL,15,Fgas-powered stations are paid to fire  
OL,16,Fup. The cost is passed on to consumers.
OL,18,FThe government said major reforms will 
OL,19,Fhalve the time it takes to build energy
OL,20,Fnetworks to cope with extra wind power.
